The remediation text makes the intended contracts precise. I’m now checking the actual enforcement boundaries separately: JSON Schema admissibility, append-time chain-state checks, and scorer-side defense-in-depth, since a gap in any one of those can make the retry protocol either unusable or order-sensitive.
